data.description: Looking for a new home without the new price points, well look no further. Welcome to Heritage Bay subdivision. This 3 bedroom 2 full bathroom home has everything a new homebuyer is looking for. Lets start with the updated high end appliances located in the kitchen, right below the speakers in the ceiling. The open floor plan allows you to watch TV while the fireplace is burning. Home has been freshly painted, LVP flooring throughout home, not including bedrooms. Imagine the warm summer nights sitting in your backyard sipping wine under your covered porch. No need to worry about privacy, home comes with a fence.. And last but not least, lets not forget about the two car garage , tankless water heater, and the huge laundry room. Huge lot. Property line is adjacent to property as well.
